# =============================================================================
# MASTER BLOCK - Ignore Everything Else
# =============================================================================
# Remove this section when copying to a project, then add whitelist rules
# Example:
#   !*.go
#   !go.mod
#   !go.sum
#   !*.md
#   !*/
# =============================================================================

!*.md
!Formula/*.rb
!*/
!.gitignore
!.github/workflows/*.yaml
!.github/workflows/*.yml

# Keep directory structure visible
!*/
